description: TwinCAT3 commenting standards. Mandatory I/O comments, block section separators, FB headers. Enforces consistent documentation style using (* *) comment syntax exclusively.
globs: "**/*.TcPOU,**/*.TcDUT,**/*.TcGVL,**/*.TcIO"
